name: 3D Platformer FInal (TheAsianCow)
description:
Here is my final version of the 3D platformer

The modifications are: 

Whole new different level designs for each level.

Each level has a unique of reaching the end goal

Complex timing jumps using platforms, pistons, enemies, and jump pads

Different key coded keycards

Some amplified enemies.

One of my proposed modifications was based on changing music, but I sadly didn't get enough time in creating that.

~Credit to Ethan Plemmons
